-- 2012-01-23T05:09:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-23/hospitality-property-may-undergo-rights-offer-as-absa-debt-facility-ends.html
Hospitality Property Fund Ltd. said
it may need to sell shares to existing investors to reduce its
debt levels and is still in talks with  Absa Group Ltd. (ASA)  and other
funders about a 1.35 billion rand facility that expires next
month.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
